0.100.0 -> 0.101.0
=====================
* Soname is bumped again due to API clean up and new APIs.
* Bug Fixes
  * Issue#7: Invalid dump for short description.
  * warning messages on monitoring files
  * RHBZ#450574: Fix a typo in imsettings-restart.
* Features
